sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant PC as ProductController
    participant PS as ProductService
    participant AC as ApiClient
    participant API as External API

    U->>PC: GET /products/{id}
    PC->>PS: getProduct(id)
    PS->>AC: get("/products/{id}")
    AC->>API: GET /api/products/{id}
    API-->>AC: { data: { id, name, image, images[], pricing_tiers[], ... } }
    AC-->>PS: Response
    PS-->>PC: array

    PC->>PS: getRelatedProducts(productId, categoryId)
    PS->>PS: getProducts(page: 1, categoryId: [categoryId])
    PS->>AC: get("/products", { category_id, per_page })
    AC->>API: GET /api/products?category_id[]=X
    API-->>AC: { data: [...products] }
    AC-->>PS: Response
    PS->>PS: filter out current product
    PS-->>PC: array

    PC-->>U: Inertia::render("product/show", { product, relatedProducts })

    Note over U: product/show.tsx renders ImageGallery
    Note over U: User taps image → opens ImageModal
    Note over U: ImageModal supports swipe, pinch-to-zoom, dots
    Note over U: Related products shown in horizontal carousel
    Note over U: User taps related product → navigates to that product
